Class PushChangesPlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.model.PushChangesPlan

  • public class PushChangesPlan
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds parameters of a planned LiveEdit push operation. This object could be used in LiveEdit action or preview implementation. This class is going to become more complicated when we support compound scripts.
